                  <decoDesc>
                     <decoNote>Fols. 1b-2a with decorated headpiece in gold, red, blue, green, and
                        pink, and floral margins. Every folio has an inner text-box border in blue,
                        red, black, and gold. Outer border in gold. Text written within gold cloud
                        bands throughout. Many paintings.</decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <bindingDesc>
                     <p>Half-bound in dark-brown leather and brown cloth. Gold borders on leather.
                        Spine has 5 bands as well as gold decoration. Title "Indian System of
                        Hawking" given on spine.</p>
                  </bindingDesc>
